overview:
CDROM2GO.COM, the world’s most comprehensive site for CD, DVD, and USB duplication products and services.

Their media storage products include a complete line of blank recordable media, from CD and DVD to Blu-ray. They also carry a complete line of duplication equipment such as stand-alone duplication towers, disc printers, publishers, recorders, and much more. All of their USDM products are professional grade and are 100% satisfaction guaranteed.

They offer professional duplication of CD, DVD, and Blu-ray discs from hundreds to thousands of pieces. When a thousand pieces just aren’t enough, they offer full service manufacturing for discs and packaging. Using state of the art equipment, their replication specialists have developed CD / DVD manufacturing processes that ensure the highest quality products with fast turn times.
